data.name: 【SG】 PBT Dye Sublimation Keycap Set (108 Keys) - OEM Profile
data.description:
Local SG Seller – Fast Delivery – Buy with Confidence!
Note: Keycaps only, keyboard not included.
Transform your bland and boring keyboard into an Instagram-worthy one! These keycap sets are truly special. Guaranteed to bring your keyboard and setup to life with its vibrant color scheme and radiant colors.
【COMPATIBILITY】
Fits most mechanical keyboards and optical keyboards that use Cherry MX switches or Cherry-like switches such as Gateron, Kailh, Outemu, and more.
【PBT Dye-Sub】
This set of keycaps is made of high-quality PBT materials, and the thickness is about 1.5 mm, which is very durable. In addition, dye-sublimation technology is used to print fonts and exquisite patterns on the keycaps. These fonts and patterns are very clear and not easy to fall off.
【OEM PROFILE】
The most popular OEM profile keycaps have sculpted shapes that conform to your fingertips to increase comfort during typing or gaming.
【Keyboard Layout】
Compatible with 61/87/104 keys standard US/ANSI mechanical keyboard whose spacebar is 6.25u (around 11.7cm), and 1.25u bottom modifier keys. This keycap set is not compatible with 64/68/71/72/82/84 keys mechanical keyboard layout. This is also not compatible with non-standard bottom row layouts such as Razer Huntsman Elite (6.0u spacebar) or Corsair K70/Logitech G710+ (6.5u spacebar).
【Specification】
Material: PBT
Thickness: ~1.5 mm
Legend: Dye Sublimation
Backlit: No
Layout: US/ANSI 108 keys
Profile: OEM Profile
